  <title>Reference Geometry</title>
  <keywords>
    <keyword>Reference Geometry</keyword>
  </keywords>
  <body>
    <para styleclass="Popup Box"><table styleclass="PopupTable" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Reference Geometry</text> is a sketch-element that is copied onto the <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Base-Part</text> in the active <text styleclass="Popup Box2">Mechanism-Editor</text> from a <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Part</text> in a different <text styleclass="Popup Box2">Mechanism-Editor.</text> If you edit or move the source sketch-element, the <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Reference Geometry</text> in the active <text styleclass="Popup Box2">Mechanism-Editor</text> also updates to the new size or position. Reference-Geometry updates dynamically.</para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
